The paper deals with image restoration using convolutional neural networks, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The use of neural networks for estimation and restoration also falls under machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also involves image processing (cs.MM) and information retrieval (cs.IR) as it deals with the restoration of degraded images.
